<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id62cd2560-4962-11f1-add1-b56d3fa293fa" identifier="/us/usc/t25/s4117"><num value="4117">§ 4117.</num><heading> Authorization of appropriations</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">There are authorized to be appropriated for grants under this subchapter such sums as may be necessary for each of fiscal years 2009 through 2013. This section shall take effect on <date date="1996-10-26">October 26, 1996</date>.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id62cd2561-4962-11f1-add1-b56d3fa293fa">(<ref href="/us/pl/104/330/tI/s108">Pub. L. 104–330, title I, § 108</ref>, <date date="1996-10-26">Oct. 26, 1996</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/110/4030">110 Stat. 4030</ref>; <ref href="/us/pl/107/292/s2/a">Pub. L. 107–292, § 2(a)</ref>, <date date="2002-11-13">Nov. 13, 2002</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/116/2053">116 Stat. 2053</ref>; <ref href="/us/pl/110/411/tVII/s701/a">Pub. L. 110–411, title VII, § 701(a)</ref>, <date date="2008-10-14">Oct. 14, 2008</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/122/4334">122 Stat. 4334</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
<notes type="uscNote" id="id62cd2562-4962-11f1-add1-b56d3fa293fa">
